\p
\v 9 ¶ Furthermore he \w made|strong="H6213"\w* the \w court|strong="H2691"\w* of the \w priests|strong="H3548"\w*, and the \w great|strong="H1419"\w* \w court|strong="H5835"\w*, and \w doors|strong="H1817"\w* for the \w court|strong="H5835"\w*, and \w overlaid|strong="H6823"\w* the \w doors|strong="H1817"\w* of them with \w brass|strong="H5178"\w*.  
